data.description: Have you been looking for a home in the desirable city of Novi? Look no further! This generously sized brick ranch offers quite a bang for your buck.  Sitting on just under a quarter of an acre lot, this home offers almost 1,400 square feet of indoor living space, an open concept living room/kitchen bar/dining room combo, a huge, relaxing, 3 seasons room with all new screens, a sizeable, fenced in, private, back yard, new paint, new flooring in bedrooms and family room, electric window coverings, and tons of natural light.  Conveniently located near restaurants, shopping, entertainment. Just minutes from Novi High School and 12 Oaks Mall. Come and see for yourself!  Buyer's agent to verify all listing data.
